Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,字幕制作翻译：goodliuwu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,生 死 时 速  （速度）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\1c&H12D7ED&\b0}警告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an6}（地下室入口）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，这地方是禁区\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hey, this area's restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，对，我知道\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hi. Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们叫我下来的，有电线坏了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}They called me down here. Some of this wiring got screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没人打电话下来告诉我\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Nobody called it down to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要看看工单\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I'm gonna have to see a work order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好，等一会\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah. Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是冲你来的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，我看这样就行，做得好，大家\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Well, I guess that wraps it up. Good work, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂，这样处理我再高兴没有了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Marty, I couldn't be happier with the way this worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦，等一等  - 喔\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Hold that. - Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,吉，谢谢\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Gee. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你按按钮，鲍勃\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Thanks for pushing that, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,灯亮了，但你永远不知道，它真的可能是坏的!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The light's on, but you never know, it really might be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不！拜托！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}No. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,天!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃，你按了什么键？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Bob, what button did you push?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得，快点\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Peter, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,巴格韦尔先生，确保另外两部电梯锁上，而且没人\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Mr Bagwell, make sure these other elevators remain locked down and empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，这里没有别的路\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Now, there's other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没有门，没有其它进出口，除了检修板，清楚了吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}No doors, no other way in or out, except through access panels, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好了先生们，我们这儿有13个乘客被困高速电梯\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}All right, gentlemen, what we have here are 13 passengers in an express elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,30楼下方\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}below floor 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹已炸断线缆，炸弹客要三百万，否则炸掉紧急刹车装置\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Bomb's already taken out cables. Bomber wants $3 million or he blows the emergencie brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少时间？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What's our clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他给了一小时\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He gave one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们还剩正好23分钟\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}That leaves us 23 minutes exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么东西能让这电梯不掉下来？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Anything else to keep this elevator from falling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，地下室\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,市政厅希望能避免最后变成那样，特拉文\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The city hall like to avoid that would end up, Traven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能救出乘客吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We can't just unload the passengers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是高速电梯，先生们\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}This is an express elevator, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一进出方法是通过检修口，炸弹客也给盖口接了线触发炸弹\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The only way in or out is through access panels. The bomber's also wired the hatch to trigger the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这说明他是“虽然疯狂但不笨”的类型\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}which seats him in the "crazy but not stupid" section.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，哈利自愿去检查那个设备\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Sir, Harry volunteers to examine the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对，是的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好，你两个去看看\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Fine. The two of you check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,最近的检修口在大堂32楼\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The nearest access panel's on the 32nd floor in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要报告，我们处于等待状态\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I want reports only. We're in a holding pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沃西、布里格斯，我要你们警戒地下区出入情况\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Worthy, Briggs, I want you to secure the base area you know, when in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,其他所有人，我要你们负责大楼疏散\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Everyone else, I want you to affirm building evac.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,行动\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们要用走的了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Looks like we're walkin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 赶快，但要小心脚下  - 29楼\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Hurry, but watch your step.  - 29
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一路下到大堂\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}All the way down to the lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走，大伙儿\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Let's go, folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,30楼\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}30.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,31楼\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}31.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,32楼\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}32.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哈罗？  - 什么情况\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Hello?  - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快啊，把我们弄出去！  - 哈罗\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Come on, man. Get us out of here.  - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了？  - 哈罗\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- What's up?  - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,救命！拜托，救我们出去!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Help! Please! Get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,救我们出去!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在上面？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Who's up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在上面？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Who's up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0} What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们，这是洛杉矶警方\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Ladies and gentlemen, this is the LAPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢天谢地  - 你们在上面干什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Thank God. - What are you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是电梯故障，别紧张就好\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}There's been an elevator malfunction, so just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，赶紧啊，你们还等什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hey, come on! What are you guys waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽快救你们出去\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We'll have you out of there as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我在扯谎吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Am I lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么派警察来？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}How come they sent cops here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不是应该派修理员来吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Shouldn't they send repair guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是专家，我只是干活的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You're the expert. I just work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来相当牢固\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Looks pretty solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们认识的什么人吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Anyone we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我没认出手法，但他是行家\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I don't recognise the work, but he's a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他时间卡得很紧\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's cutting it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢这样\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对，有什么喜不喜欢的？麦克说等，我们就等\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah. Well, what's to like? Mac said we hold, so we hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，突击发问\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}All right, pop quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,机场，枪手有一名人质，他用她当掩护，快上飞机了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The airport. Gunman with one hostage. He's using her for cover. He's almost to a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在100英尺外\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You're 100 feet away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,开枪打人质\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Shoot the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,把她脱离状况\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Take her out of the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,造成轻伤，他就不能带她上飞机了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Go for the good wound and he can't get to the plane with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一枪命中\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Clear shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你内心是个疯子，你知道吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You're deeply nuts, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,“开枪打人质”\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}"Shoot the hostage. "
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利，不对头\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Harry, this is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他不管怎样都会引爆\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's gonna blow it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，直觉\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I don't know. Gut feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,目前麦克的官阶高于你的直觉，我们等吧\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Right now Mac outranks your gut, so we sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这太久了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}This is taking way too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得那电梯有多重？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}How much d'you think that elevator weighs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，得了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以对那些人质干点什么\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Maybe we can do something about those hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会开枪打他们，对吧？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We're not gonna shoot 'em, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，你们去哪儿？怎么了？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hey, where you going? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要走！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要把我们丢在这里\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Don't leave us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,（屋顶/53）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我们只要把他们脱离状况\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}No, we just take them out of the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定它能拉住吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Are you sure it'll hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,会拉住的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It'll hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,六分钟\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Six minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能争取更多时间，他不答话！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I can't get any more time. He's not talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就要那该死的钱!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I need the goddamn money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再跟我说一次，哈利\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Tell me again, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我干嘛做这份工作？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Why did I take this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,得了，再干30年，你领到微薄退休金和一只廉价金表\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, come on. 30 more years of this, you get a tiny pension and a cheap gold watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,酷\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,停\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,天， 这儿真热\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}God, it's hot in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没有空气\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}There's no air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们就不能撬开门吗?  - 我喘不上气\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Can't they just pry the doors open? - I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跟老子瞎搞\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Don't fuck with Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,通常现在他们已掉下来\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Usually they fall down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他提前了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这狗娘养的提前了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The son of a bitch is early!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，我们这儿需要帮手，快\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Mac, we need more help up here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你！我不想死！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, please! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,求你救我们\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Please save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,开门！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,开门！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会救你们出去\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We'll get you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把手给我!  - 就这样，继续\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Give me your hands! - That's it, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没关系的，把手给我  - 拉我过去\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- It's okay. Give me your hands. - Pull me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 小心头！小心头！  - 救救我\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Watch your head. Watch your head. - Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了，我抓住你了  - 慢点\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Okay, I've got you. - Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦，谢谢你  - 你没事了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Oh, thank you.  - You'r fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事了  - 哦，谢谢你\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- You'r fine.  - Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 带她走  - 下一个是谁？快\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Take her.  - Who's next？Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,接到你了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,退后，退后\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Step back. Step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是在搞什么鬼？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What the hell is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我们，赶快\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Help us, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快，走走！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hurry up, go go go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们走！  - 来，来\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Let's go.  - Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老天，带我出去！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小心头！小心头！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Watch yout head. Watch yout head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，女士，来!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on, lady! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不！不！  - 来吧，女士，来!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- No No.  - Come on, lady! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住我的手！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Grab my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，我们走\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不！我不能！  - 要掉下去了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- No, I can't!  - It's going to fall
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就走一步，过来拉住我的手\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Just take one step, reach out and take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:16:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,天，别放开我\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, God! Don't let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得好玩吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Was it good for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我很开心，你感觉呢，亲？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It was great for me. How was it for you, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 电梯掉了  - 好，很高兴知道\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}-Elevator dropped. -Good. That's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的表慢了吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Is your watch slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我不知道，他提早起跑，我们还剩3分钟\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, I don't know. He jumped the gun. We had three minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他干嘛这样做？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Why does he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,让他损失了三百万\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's losing his $3 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，也许他把持不了足够长的时间\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I don't know. Maybe he couldn't hold his wad long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这在中年男人当中是个普遍问题\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It's a common problem among middle-aged men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这么听说的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}So I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这里\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能是在伯克伊玛引爆那东西的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He could've blown that thing from Pacoima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道我们在做什么事\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He knew we were up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在附近\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会躲在某个角落，我们已疏散大厦，得了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's not gonna corner himself in a building we evacuated anyway. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他会…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他会想要留在这儿，但他也要四处活动，对吧？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}he'd wanna be here, but he'd wanna stay mobile, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,电梯\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,客用电梯都停了，他们查看过\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Passenger cars were stopped. They checked 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,货用电梯呢？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What about the freight elevators?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能请神秘嘉宾来签到吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Will the mystery guest please sign in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,到边上去\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Get to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕！糟糕！糟糕！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Shit! Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,起来！ 给我起来！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Up! Get your ass up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不会有人为了你 付给我三百万吧？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I don't suppose anybody'll give me three million just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,慢着！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,突击发问，高手\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Pop quiz, hotshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怖分子挟持警察人质，胸前绑黄色炸药，够把大厦炸掉一半\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Terrorist holding a police hostage. Got enough dynamite strapped to his chest to blow a building in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你怎样做？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Now what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,地下一层会有50个警察等着你\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}There's gonna be 50 cops waiting for you in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,标准侧翼攻击部署，是吗？也许我们会从三楼下去\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Standard flanking deployment, right? Maybe we'll get off on the third floor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,至少他们以为如此\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}At least that's what they'll think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要定位那该死的枪声！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I want location on those goddamn shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,布里格斯，杰克和哈利在哪里？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Briggs! Where's Jack and Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,警督，货用电梯在动\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Lieutenant, we've got movement on the freight elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在三楼，我们走\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It's on three. Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一站\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}End of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真是失望，我不介意这么说\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}This day has been real disappointing, I don't mind saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？因为你没机会杀了大家？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What? Because you didn't get to kill everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天，小子，你会希望从未见过我\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}There will come a time, boy, when you'll wish you'd never met me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，就是今天了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Mister, I'm already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没看见这里我管事吗？我扔掉这操纵杆…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Didn't you see I'm in charge here? I drop this stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就得用抹布把你的朋友收拾起来\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}and they pick your friend up with a sponge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你准备去死了吗，朋友？  - 操你妈\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}-Are you ready to die, friend? -Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，二百年时间…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}In 200 years
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就从“我后悔只有一次生命为国奉献” {\fs12}[内森·黑尔名言]{\r}\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}we've come from "I regret but I have one life to give for my country"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,到“操你妈”了？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}to "fuck you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊，扔了那操纵杆，来啊\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Go ahead. Drop the stick. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，哈利\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Shut up, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，世上最有种的人都到齐了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We've got all the balls in the world right here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧，你无路可逃\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Give it up. You got nowhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,开枪打人质\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Shoot the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说再见，哈利\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Say goodbye, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别动！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧！你没有选择了！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Give it up! You're out of options!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.95,0:23:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,通过献身和英勇，下面这两位警官成功解救了...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Through dedication and bravery, these next two officers effected the rescue...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.56,0:23:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城市的13位市民\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}of 13 citizens of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢他们两位…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}And, thanks to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怖分子的炸弹唯一夺走的只是他自己的命\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}the only life taken by the terrorist's bomb was his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我开枪，我不敢相信\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You shot me. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们给你发奖章表彰对我开枪，你这衰人\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}They're giving you a medal for shooting me, you little prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.34,0:23:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利，你叫我做的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Harry, you told me to.
