Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.65,0:26:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你听过没有？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Do you ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.55,0:26:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不会总是在旁边掩护你...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Because I am not gonna be around to back you up...
