Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.00,0:29:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.40,0:29:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我没准备吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You think I wouldn't have been prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.80,0:29:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,两年时间，我花费来设计那件电梯案\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Two years I spent setting up that elevator job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.57,0:29:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,两年时间，我全心投入\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Two years I invested myself in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.51,0:29:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能明白我的那种奉献\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You couldn't understand the kind of commitment that I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.81,0:29:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你破坏了别人一生的工作...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You ruined a man's life's work...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.68,0:29:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,而你以为你能一走了之吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}and you think you can walk away?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.16,0:29:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你戴着眼罩看不清世情\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You got blinders on to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.54,0:29:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我现在已引起你注意，对吗，杰克?\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}but I got your attention now, didn't I, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.52,0:29:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不冲我来?\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Why didn't you just come after me?
