Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.44,0:29:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会收取\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}which I will collect.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.07,0:29:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,370万美元\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}$3.7 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.94,0:29:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的储备金，杰克，在我这个年纪，你就得想在前头\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It's my nest egg, Jack. At my age, you gotta think ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.38,0:29:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等我找到你...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}When I find you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.54,0:29:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,突击发问，高手\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Pop quiz, hotshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.31,0:29:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一辆巴士上有个炸弹\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}There's a bomb on a bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.95,0:29:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦巴士时速达50英里...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Once the bus goes 50 miles an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.58,0:29:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹就启动\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}the bomb is armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.26,0:30:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只要它减速到50英里以下...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}If it drops below 50...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.09,0:30:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就会爆炸\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}it blows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.96,0:30:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么办？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.69,0:30:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么办？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.78,0:30:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要知道是哪辆巴士?\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I'd wanna know what bus it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.53,0:30:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我会告诉你?\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You think I'm gonna tell you that?
