Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.35,1:00:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能死在这儿\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I can't die here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.55,1:00:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，闭嘴，哥们\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hey, shut up, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.93,1:00:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个妻子\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I got a wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.21,1:00:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，是吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.47,1:00:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.63,1:00:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你有妻子，我没有，是不是说我就该死？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}So if you have a wife and I don't, does that mean I'm expendable?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.93,1:00:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么，哥们?\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What are you talking about, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.54,1:00:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙只是在乱说\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The guy's just talking crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.82,1:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他让我紧张，让大家紧张\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He gets on my nerves, gets on everybody's nerves.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.91,1:00:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？我觉得我有权沮丧\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I think I have the right to be a little upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.04,1:00:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那你又瞪什么瞪，老兄？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What are you staring at, anyway, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.68,1:01:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不让大家安静地死，反正都是死\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Why don't you let us all die in peace, if it has to happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.55,1:01:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是硬汉，啊？你还真是硬汉子？  - 我有权沮丧\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Oh, so you're a really tough guy, huh?  - I have the right to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.25,1:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们干嘛不出去解决？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Why don't we just step outside?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.57,1:01:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样？ 你没事吧？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}How are you doing? You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.84,1:01:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做点什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.71,1:01:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,当炸弹爆炸时…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}When that bomb went off...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.08,1:01:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.08,1:01:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为就这样了，就是这个炸弹\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I thought that was it. I thought that was the bomb
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.17,1:01:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而我已死了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}and I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.97,1:01:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,后来我看见她的尸体落下巴士，就像是…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}And then when I saw her body fall under the bus, it was like...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.54,1:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你高兴自己仍然活着\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You were glad you were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.26,1:01:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我真抱歉\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.46,1:01:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不用\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.90,1:01:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该高兴，我们都应该\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You should be glad. We all are.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.40,1:01:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这不表示你不关心\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It doesn't mean you don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.91,1:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，但她太害怕了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I know, but she was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.83,1:02:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她是害怕了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}she was scared
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.88,1:02:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个好人，不该被杀\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}She was a nice lady who didn't deserve to get killed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.25,1:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是安妮，如果她下了车，可能会害死我们大家\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}but if she'd gotten off, it would have killed us all.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.35,1:02:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他才是混蛋，安妮\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's the asshole, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.42,1:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那个置我们于绝境的人，记住，好吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The guy who put us here. Remember that, Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.85,1:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大混蛋\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Big asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.37,1:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.63,1:02:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.86,1:02:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有多远？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}well, how far?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.87,1:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，我们有个大难题\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Sir, we have a serious problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.60,1:02:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.54,1:02:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这条高速未完成\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}This freeway isn't finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.81,1:02:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.14,1:02:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,空中单位看到了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The aerial unit caught it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.49,1:02:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大概三英里前方有一段空缺\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}About three miles ahead there's a section missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.45,1:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一段空缺？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}A section missing?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.32,1:02:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但在地图上是有的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}But it's on the map.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.19,1:02:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,地图上是他妈完成了的！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It's finished on the goddam map!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.39,1:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是进度落后了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I guess they fell behind
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.90,1:02:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,操！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.36,1:02:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你被炒鱿鱼了！大家都他妈的被炒了！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You're fired. Everybody's fucking fired!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.30,1:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,带我靠近些\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Get me closer!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.14,1:03:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，靠近些，在镜子里看着他\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hey, get closer. Watch him in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.94,1:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.24,1:03:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那一段有多大？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}How big is the section?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.98,1:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,50英尺 {\fs12}[15米]{\r}，至少\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}50 feet... at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.29,1:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,前面的路上有个缺口\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}There's a gap in the road up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.87,1:03:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很大\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It's big.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.16,1:03:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你在开玩笑， 多大？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You're kidding. How big?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.02,1:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,50英尺\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}50 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.10,1:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰克  - 什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Jack.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.63,1:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须设法让这些人下来\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We gotta get these people off the bus somehow.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.38,1:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我不能的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You know I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.64,1:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他说什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.31,1:03:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.14,1:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，他说什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack, what did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.24,1:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事?\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.42,1:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,公路上有个缝隙\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}There's a gap in the freeway.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.26,1:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.52,1:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你什么意思？  - 空隙能有多大？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- What do you mean?  - How big is a gap?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.92,1:03:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他说了吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.59,1:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,50英尺\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}50 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.15,1:04:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,前面几英里处\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}A couple of miles ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.60,1:04:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这太疯狂了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}This is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.40,1:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 老天  - 杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Jiz.  - Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.80,1:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.94,1:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我换到空挡让发动机空转怎么样？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What if I shift into neutral and just keep the engine revving?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.64,1:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行，他已经想到了   - 那怎么办？怎么办？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- No, he'd have thought of that. - What, then? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.61,1:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦，我的天啊  - 怎么办？杰克？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Oh, my God.  - What? Jack?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.94,1:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 地板油  - 什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Floor it.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.62,1:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,踩地板油\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Floor it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.45,1:04:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一座立交桥，可能有斜坡，踩尽油门\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It's an interchange. There might be an incline. Floor it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.85,1:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.46,1:04:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大家抓住座位，或者能抓什么抓什么\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Everybody hold onto your seats or whatever you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.03,1:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在过空隙时，头低下\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}When we hit the gap, heads down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.50,1:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样？就这样？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}That's it? That's it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.83,1:04:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只能做到这样\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}That's all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.04,1:04:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,把这些放在座位下面\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Let's put these underneath your seat, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.80,1:04:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把你们的包放在座位下面\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Put your bags underneath the seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.05,1:04:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，我不是有意开枪打那个人的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hey, I didn't mean to shoot the guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.71,1:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,坐稳\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.78,1:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这样真的有作用吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Is this really gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.86,1:05:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.26,1:05:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.56,1:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.14,1:05:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧，来吧！  - 老天\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Come on. Come on.  - God.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.84,1:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧，来吧！  - 老天\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Come on. Come on.  - God.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.80,1:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.85,1:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,老天\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}God!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.26,1:05:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，糟糕，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, shit, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.74,1:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大家抓紧！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Everybody hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.55,1:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（前路封闭）
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.35,1:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，天啊\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.06,1:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.86,1:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.81,1:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们做到了！  - 好呀！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- We made it!  - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.31,1:06:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们完全控制住了！！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We are way under controle
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.36,1:07:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗？  - 对\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- You okay?   - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.75,1:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吧？  - 我还好，我还好\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- You okay?   - I'm okay. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.68,1:07:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好了!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.91,1:07:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,诺伍德，我们走!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Norwood, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.21,1:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 人人都没事吧？  - 对\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Is everybody Okay? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.87,1:07:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.87,1:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.43,1:07:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你真行，安妮！你真行！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You're the man, Annie. You are the man!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.76,1:07:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢  多谢你们\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Thank you. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.27,1:07:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你埋没了天份\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I think you missed your calling.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.72,1:07:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？什么天份？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah? What was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.60,1:07:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看路\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Watch the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.20,1:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该当飞行员\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You should have been a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.05,1:07:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下高速\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Get off.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.95,1:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.45,1:07:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里下，现在，从这里下\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Get off this. Now. Get off this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.45,1:07:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,（洛杉矶机场出口）
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.80,1:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,进里面\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}In there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.59,1:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那里？就这里？  - 对\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Where? Right here? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.57,1:07:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就这儿?   - 对\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Right here? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.90,1:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,（所有车辆一律检查）
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.50,1:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,停车！等等\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Stop! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.02,1:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚驶进了机场\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's just entered the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.29,1:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊  - 机场？那儿有好几千人\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- All right!  - The airport? There's thousands of people there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.74,1:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,正是我家杰克，他可以在跑道上兜圈，给我们赚点时间\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}That's my boy Jack. He can circle the runways and buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.31,1:08:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,直升机不能飞进去，是限航空域\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Choppers can't fly in there. It's restricted space.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.88,1:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他正往机坪尽头那边去\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's headed for the end of the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.11,1:08:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那一定是布拉沃探戈，一条紧急跑道\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}That must be Bravo Tango, an emergency runway.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.58,1:08:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好，希望已建好，我们走！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah, let's hope it's built. Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.63,1:08:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在机场\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We're at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.27,1:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊，怎么了？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah? So?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.43,1:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经看过机场了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I already seen the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.43,1:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.39,1:09:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,非常，非常刺激，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Very, very exciting, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.34,1:09:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就差一点，嗯？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Some close calls, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.60,1:09:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你做得很好\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}But you've done all right for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.67,1:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你要什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.93,1:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我要钱  杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I want money, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.10,1:09:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我但愿我有更高尚的目的，但是…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I wish I had some loftier purpose but...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.37,1:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕到头来还是钱的事情，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I'm afraid in the end it's just the money, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.24,1:09:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I would like...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.18,1:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不连号码的大钞，装在两个干净的塑料袋里...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}large non-sequential bills in two clear plastic bags...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.31,1:09:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没记号的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}unmarked.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.72,1:09:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这些你都能记下吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Can you remember all that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.76,1:09:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我干什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What are you telling me for?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.65,1:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我要你帮我去拿，别搞晚了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Because I want you to help me to get it before it gets too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.70,1:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌谈判专家，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I hate negotiators, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.49,1:09:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们好像是你的好朋友一样跟你谈话…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}They talk to you like they're your best friend...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.76,1:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可他们根本不认识你\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}and they don't even know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.69,1:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们干嘛跟我乱来？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Why are they messing with me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.25,1:09:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以为我做这些都是为了好玩吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Do they think I'm doing this for fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.40,1:09:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.67,1:09:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，那不公平，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, that's unfair, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.04,1:10:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道我对此事的感受\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You don't know how I feel about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.84,1:10:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你甚至不认识我\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You don't even know me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.61,1:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你想捞一大票不是你挣来的钱\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You want a shitload of money you didn't earn.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.92,1:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，是我挣来的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, I earned it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.11,1:10:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了一生挣来的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I spent my life earning it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.68,1:10:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有一枚奖章，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I got a medal, too, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.45,1:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一枚奖章和一张解雇书…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}a medal and a pink slip
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.82,1:10:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一句“为你的手而遗憾”\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}and a "sorry about your hand".
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.35,1:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须让我下车\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You have to let me off.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.86,1:10:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，不，那可不好\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, no. That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.00,1:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我帮助你吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.29,1:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要跟这些人面对面说，他们以为你在胡说\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I need to talk to these people face to face. They think you're bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.50,1:10:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有那么想\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}They don't think that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.53,1:10:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧，你要钱，我不想再有人死\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}LoOkay, you want the money, I don't want anyone else to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.90,1:10:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,让我到地面上去\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Let me get on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.20,1:10:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我，这没违反规则\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Just me. That's not against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.58,1:10:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我要你尽快回去\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}All right. I want you back real fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.82,1:10:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.43,1:10:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，别玩花样，你知道我占上风\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack, nothing tricky now. You know that I'm on top of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.45,1:10:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要试图自作聪明\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Do not attempt to grow a brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.40,1:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜想现在有个计划了？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}So I guess there's a plan now?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.56,1:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Could be.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.20,1:11:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗？   - 他要让我下车\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Yeah? - He's letting me off.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.54,1:11:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.60,1:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,持续绕圈，你会没事的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Just keep circling. You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.54,1:11:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家坐稳，我要离开一会儿\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Everybody sit tight. I'm getting off for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.05,1:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得这是个好主意吗？  - 没事的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Do you think that's a good idea?  -It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.25,1:11:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？你要把我们留在这儿？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What? Are you just gonna leave us here?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.10,1:11:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是我就会\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I would.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.40,1:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  我不会走远\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Don't worry. I won't go far.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.55,1:11:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.15,1:11:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了我们\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Don't forget about us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.60,1:11:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,直升机都走了，杰克，我们这就放乘客下车吧\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}The choppers are gone, Jack. Let's dump the passengers now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.08,1:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，他有所准备\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}No way. He's ready for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.51,1:11:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么可能？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.67,1:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么做的，麦克，我只知道他会\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I don't know how, Mac. I just know he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.83,1:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直都次次领先一步\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's been a step ahead every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.78,1:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们下乘客，他会干掉他们，我敢担保\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}If we unload, he'll take them out. I guarantee.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.90,1:11:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那把我们置于何地？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}So where does that put us?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.26,1:11:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须试试拆除那炸弹\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I have to try and dismantle that bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.00,1:11:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}经过惊险行驶，从10号高速，到洛杉矶的街道…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}After an incredible ride on the 10 freeway. the streets of Los Angeles
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.39,1:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}已经105号高速…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}and the 105 freeway...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.39,1:12:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这辆巴士最后来到这里，洛杉矶国际机场\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}this bus has ended up here at Los Angeles International Airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.86,1:12:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在跑道上兜圈\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}circling the runway.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.24,1:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,钱不是一切（是啊，对）
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.56,1:12:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你，安妮，他在什么地方爽着呢\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I'm telling you, Annie, he's somewhere jerking off.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.31,1:12:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他一开始就不必上这辆巴士，奥提斯\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He didn't have to get on the bus in the first place, Ortiz.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.21,1:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，屁股挪到黄线外\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Get your ass behind the yellow line.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.82,1:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.86,1:12:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我毫无头绪\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.26,1:12:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有能力稳住这东西很久\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We won't be able to hold this thing steady for very long.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.73,1:12:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要几分钟，如果到时候办不到那就根本办不到了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I just need a few minutes. If I can't do it by then, I can't do it at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.37,1:12:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利，听到我吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Harry, you with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.61,1:12:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在，你小心，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah. You be careful, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.25,1:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他在干什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.01,1:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我的天，他疯了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, my God. He is insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.20,1:13:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，杰克，就这样\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Okay, Jack, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.60,1:13:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要丢了命\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Don't get dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.30,1:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是个很好的计划\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}This is not a very good plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.86,1:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要有信心，姐\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Have faith, sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.01,1:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，天啊!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.56,1:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,稳住它就行了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Just keep it steady.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.94,1:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，谢谢你提醒，奥提斯\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Thank you for the tip, Ortiz.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.20,1:13:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这人疯了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}This guy is nuts!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.11,1:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，我们试试把遥控器电池接旁路\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Okay, we'll try to bypass the remote current with the battery.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.54,1:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你能找到遥控器的引线吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Can you find the tripwire for the remote?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.58,1:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，我这里有几个选择\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I don't know. I got a few choices here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.18,1:14:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,红和黑？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Black and red?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.82,1:14:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还有绿\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}And green.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.12,1:14:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.42,1:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我会猜他不会用标准铜线做遥控\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}All right, I'm gonna guess he's not gonna go with standard copper for the remote.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.69,1:14:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那太弱了，我会用纤维合金\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}That'd be too weak. I'd use a fibre alloy.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.84,1:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，我需要你看看电线\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack, I'm gonna need you to look at the wire.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.33,1:14:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利，包住了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Harry, it's covered.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.77,1:14:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，你得剪开外层\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I know. You're gonna have to cut off the sheath.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.77,1:14:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但不要剪电线\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}But don't cut the wire.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.24,1:14:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.34,1:14:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我操\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Fuck me!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.25,1:14:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.83,1:14:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 成功了!  - 好!\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Bull's-eye! - Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.21,1:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我要你夹上电池，用铅线驳通它\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}okay. I want you to clip on the battery and then run it to the lead wire.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.07,1:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.15,1:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能旁路，会引爆\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I can't bypass. It'll fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.32,1:15:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，糟糕！是可折叠的回路\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, shit! It's a collapsible circuit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.12,1:15:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,霍华德·佩恩，亚特兰大警局拆弹组\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Howard Payne, Atlanta PD Bomb Squad.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.99,1:15:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,1989年在太阳谷退休...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Retired in Sun Valley in 1989
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.19,1:15:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,指责说自己只剩九个手指\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}when a small charge left him with fingers numbering nine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.43,1:15:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这混蛋！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}That's our scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.30,1:15:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们抓到他了，杰克，我们找到他了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We got him, Jack. We found him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.95,1:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以在15分钟内到达他家\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We can get to his place inside of 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.67,1:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了，杰克，我要你离开那里，什么也别做\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Great! Jack, i want you to get out of there and stay tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.85,1:15:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去追踪源头\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We're going after the source.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.41,1:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Watch your back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.11,1:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，等等我\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Wait...Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.15,1:15:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，把我弄出去\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Mac, get me outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.04,1:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谁去后面，看他有没有从后面出来\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Somebody go to the back and check and see if he came out the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.97,1:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快去！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.45,1:16:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看见他吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Can you see him?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.64,1:16:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在我们后面\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's not behind us.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.06,1:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.95,1:16:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在后面这儿\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's not back here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.17,1:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哦我的天，我的天，去看看！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, my God. Go look!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.92,1:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下来，看看巴士下面能否看见他\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Lay down and look under the bus and see if you can see him down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.22,1:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能看见他吗？  - 没有\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Can you see him? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.64,1:16:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你没看见他在轮胎旁边什么的吗？看看下面什么的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You don't see him back by the tyre or something? Looked under something?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.29,1:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不见他\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.15,1:16:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.20,1:16:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不见他\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.99,1:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦，天啊！我们撞到他了  - 糟糕\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Oh, my God! We hit him! - Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.30,1:16:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么鬼东西？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.89,1:16:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天，你见到他吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, my God! Do you see him?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.59,1:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们撞到他了吗？  - 看看轮胎后，看看边缘\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Did we hit him?  - Look out the back of the wheel. Look out the sides.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.20,1:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工具\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}My tools!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.13,1:17:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谁给他拿他的工具？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Will somebody get him his tools?!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.45,1:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 赶紧  - 拜托帮帮他，快点！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}- Come on.  - Please help him! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.45,1:17:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,天，我们在拖着他\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}God, we're dragging him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.52,1:17:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看见他了吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Do you see him?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.90,1:17:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪里？他在那边吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Where is he? Is he there?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.81,1:17:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见他了吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Do you see him?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.00,1:17:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.87,1:17:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.93,1:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见他了！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I see him!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.43,1:17:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.27,1:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见他了！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I see him!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.10,1:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见了？他没事吧？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You do? Is he Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.60,1:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他没事！他没事！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}He's all right! He's all right!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.25,1:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拉住我的腿！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hold my legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.55,1:17:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,拉住我的腿！来人拉住我的腿！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hold my legs. Somebody hold my legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.81,1:17:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拉住他的腿\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hold his legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.12,1:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拉住他的腿\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Hold his legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.28,1:17:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.28,1:17:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧！我抓住你了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on! I got ya!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.16,1:18:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他受伤了吗？他还好吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Is he hurt? Is he Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.96,1:18:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,拉！拉！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.56,1:18:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊！来啊！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.90,1:18:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们抓住他了，来啊，拉！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We got him now. Come on, pull!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.27,1:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,老天，我不敢相信\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jesus. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.74,1:18:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全是个疯子，你知道吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You are a complete jerk. You know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.74,1:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢老天\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.31,1:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹的事有运气吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Did you have any luck with the bomb?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.18,1:18:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有  它没爆炸\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah. It didn't go off.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.71,1:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,奥提斯，谢谢\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Ortiz, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.11,1:18:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你有多少条命啊，哥们？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}How many lives you got, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.57,1:18:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是太聪明，哥们…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You're not too bright, man...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.05,1:18:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一对又大又圆又毛的蛋蛋\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}but you got some big, round, hairy cojones.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.76,1:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这话真是…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.45,1:18:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,够恶心的，奥提斯\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}very gross, Ortiz.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.62,1:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,连赞他一句都不行\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Can't even pay him a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.10,1:18:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎样？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.72,1:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你吓屎我了，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You scared the shit out of me, Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.45,1:18:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外我很好\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Other than that, I'm fine
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.87,1:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么气味？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What is that smell?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.61,1:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是汽油\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It's gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.38,1:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在漏油？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We're leaking gas?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.54,1:18:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}We are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.05,1:19:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,（油料表）
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.20,1:19:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,咋了？你是觉得你要再来点挑战还是怎么？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}What? You felt you needed another challenge or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.23,1:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Mac
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.25,1:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克在，讲吧\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Mac here, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.19,1:19:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能找一辆加油车来？我们在漏油\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Can you get a fuel truck to pace us here? We're losing gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.23,1:19:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看能否找到，多长时间？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I'll see what I can find. How much time?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.33,1:19:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，十分钟？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}i don't know. 10 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.98,1:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不妙\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.60,1:19:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.50,1:19:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,诺伍德，赶紧弄一辆油车过来\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Norwood, get a fuel car out here on the double.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.90,1:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,行得通吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Is that gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.64,1:19:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.34,1:19:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧，哈利，救我一命\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on, Harry, save my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.97,1:21:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利，告诉我好消息，老兄\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Harry, tell me good news, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.06,1:21:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我很抱歉，杰克，他没成功\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Oh, I'm sorry, Jack. He didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.06,1:21:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你…他妈的\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.46,1:21:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是那只表引他来找我，对吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It was the watch that led him to me, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.89,1:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用我那宝贵的退休礼物来做炸弹似乎有点夸张了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It seemed a little hammy to me to build the bomb out of my precious retirement gift,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.66,1:21:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道，我琢磨弄一个标识代表“霍华德·佩恩”...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}but, you know, I figured a sign that said "Howard Payne"...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.83,1:21:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有促进作用\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}...would be pushing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.33,1:21:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要打断你他妈的脊椎骨，我对天发誓\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I'm gonna rip your fucking spine out, I swear to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.67,1:21:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你要完全照吩咐去做\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You're gonna do exactly as you're told.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.77,1:21:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，我俩都知道他是你们特殊作业中的大脑\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack, we both know that he was the brains of your particular operation.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.84,1:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你赢不了我，每一块钱你都要付给我...\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You can't beat me. You're gonna pay me every dollar.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.81,1:21:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,否则，你，那个野猫，以及那辆巴士上所有无辜的人…\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Otherwise, you, the wildcat and every innocent person on that bus...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.58,1:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都会像你朋友一样下场\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}are gonna end up just like your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.48,1:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你在注意听吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Are you paying attention?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.23,1:21:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，你在听我说吗？\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.80,1:22:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack! Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.76,1:22:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.96,1:22:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.70,1:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉他们交款处是百胜广场\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Now you tell them that the drop point is Pershing Square.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.30,1:22:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,东北角上有一个垃圾箱\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}There's a garbage can on the northeast corner.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.50,1:22:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你扔下袋子就走\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}You drop the bags and leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.28,1:22:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等你们的人都走了我才会出现\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}I don't show until all your people are gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.81,1:22:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快到11点了，杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}It's getting on to 11am, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.04,1:22:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想今天会非常美妙\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}and I think it's gonna be a very pretty day.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.96,1:22:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.86,1:22:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的，该死！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}God damn! God damn!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.07,1:22:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，杰克，好了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Come on. Jack, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.54,1:22:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别放弃我，杰克，求你了\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Don't give up on me, Jack, come on, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.34,1:22:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克，停下！\N{\fs11\1c&H4080FF&\b0}Jack, stop it!
